      • getReferenceAltitude

        public final Double getReferenceAltitude()
        The initial altitude in meters. This value can be used by a sensor implementation to augment the altitude of the sensor. For example, if you are using simulation instead of creating a 1000 m mountain model on which to place your sensor, you could instead set this value to 1000 and place your model on a ground plane with a Z height of zero.
